<manpage>
    <title> tail </title>
    <volume>Elastos常用工具</volume>

    <description>
        <para> 显示指定文件的最后n行（n为指定参数）。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <cmd_name> TAIL </cmd_name>
        <cmd_param> [-? | -n | -f filename] [filename...] </cmd_param>
    </syntax>
    <parameters>
    <param>
        <param_name>  -?  </param_name>
        <param_note> 显示帮助信息</param_note>
    </param>
    <param>
        <param_name>  -n  </param_name>
        <param_note> 显示文件的最后n行，默认为10</param_note>
    </param>
    <param>
        <param_name>  -f filename  </param_name>
        <param_note> 到文件最后并不停止，等待输入。使用-f参数时只能打开一个文件</param_note>
    </param>
    <param>
        <param_name>  filename  </param_name>
        <param_note> 文件名，可为多个文件</param_note>
    </param>
    </parameters>

    <remarks>
        <para>显示多个文件内容时在显示每个文件内容之前打印文件名。</para>
    </remarks>

    <examples>
    <example>
        <eg_line>tail -1 file1.txt</eg_line>
        <eg_note> 显示文件file1.txt的最后1行。输出结果：</eg_note>
        <eg_result><![CDATA[
the last line in file1.txt.
]]></eg_result>

    </example>
    <example>
        <eg_line>tail -1 file1.txt file2.txt  </eg_line>
        <eg_note> 显示文件file1.txt和file2.txt的最后1行。输出结果：</eg_note>
        <eg_result><![CDATA[
==> file1.txt <==
the last line in file1.txt.

==> file2.txt <==
the last line in file2.txt.
]]></eg_result>

    </example>

    </examples>

